{"word":"H3700 - כָּסַף - kâçaph - kaw-saf' - Desire","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּסַף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâçaph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-saf'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Desire"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விருப்பம் வை, ஆவலாயிரு. வாஞ்சையாயிரு, விருப்பப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to long for, to yearn for, to long after"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to long for"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to long for (deeply)"},{"paragraph":"2) being longed for (passive participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb par / வினைச்சொல் par</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to become <i>pale</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>pine</i> after; also to <i>fear: - </i>[have] desire, be greedy, long, sore."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3700 - כָּסַף - kâçaph - kaw-saf'/3700\">H3700</a>, <a href=\"#/H3701 - כֶּסֶף - keçeph - keh'-sef/3701\">H3701</a>, <a href=\"#/H3703 - כָּסִפְיָא - Kâçiphyâʼ - kaw-sif-yaw'/3703\">H3703</a>"}]}